imdb.title: Scott Sullivan's Movie Reviews
plot: Film critic Scott Sullivan reviews everything from opening day releases to classics from years past. The massive catalog of in-depth analyses is a culmination of every picture Scott has discussed. Each review is scored on a ten-point scale.
